								},
								{
									"key": "user_id",
									"value": "23"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Get travel records for a specific month and year. Both query parameters are required.\n\n**Response:**\n- `records`: Array of day-wise travel entries (including route, start/end, payout)\n- `summary`: Aggregated totals with `totalDistance`, `eligibleDistance`, `totalPayout`, and `ratePerKm`\n\n**Optional query:** `user_id` (filter results to a specific executive when used by admins)."
					},
					"response": []
				},
